4 (A) IN THIS SECTION, “PERINATAL MENTAL BEHAVIORAL HEALTH
5 CONDITION” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN § 15–830 OF THIS SUBTITLE.
6 (B) THIS SECTION APPLIES TO:
