8 PROVIDE HOSPITAL, MEDICAL, OR SURGICAL BENEFITS TO INDIVIDUALS OR GROUPS
9 ON AN EXPENSE–INCURRED BASIS UNDER HEALTH INSURANCE POLICIES OR
10 CONTRACTS THAT ARE ISSUED OR DELIVERED IN THE STATE; AND
11 (2) HEALTH MAINTENANCE ORGANIZATIONS THAT PROVIDE
12 HOSPITAL, MEDICAL, OR SURGICAL BENEFITS TO INDIVIDUALS OR GROUPS UNDER
