24 ENTITY SUBJECT TO THIS SECTION MAY SUBJECT THE COVERAGE REQUIRED UNDER
25 THIS SUBSECTION TO A COPAYMENT OR COINSURANCE REQUIREMENT OR
26 DEDUCTIBLE THAT AN ENTITY SUBJECT TO THIS SECTION IMPOSES FOR SIMILAR
27 COVERAGES UNDER THE SAME POLICY OR CONTRACT.
28 (II) THE COPAYMENT OR COINSURANCE REQUIREMENT OR
29 DEDUCTIBLE IMPOSED UNDER SUBPARAGRAPH (I) OF THIS PARAGRAPH MAY NOT BE
30 GREATER THAN THE COPAYMENT OR COINSURANCE REQUIREMENT OR DEDUCTIBLE
31 IMPOSED BY THE ENTITY FOR SIMILAR COVERAGES.

